headline: Interactive Brokers Group, Inc. (IBKR) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Interactive Brokers (IBKR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +14.00% and +12.85%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: MarketAxess to Host Conference Call Announcing Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results on Friday, November 7, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, October 16, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX) the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, will issue a press release announcing its third quarter 2025 financial results on Friday, November 7, 2025, before the market opens. Chris Concannon, Chief Executive Officer, and Ilene Fiszel Bieler, Chief Financial Officer, will host a conference call to provide a strategic update and discuss the Company’s financial results and outlook on Friday
